messages.message: Sure thing Brian, how are you?
I'm super. What are you working on at 360?
We work on NetSuite. Have you used Netsuite before?
I wouldn't say that... ;) it's all javascript and platform apis. What are you up to?
Writing a site in Node.js and some security stuff.
Network admin automation using PowerShell.  Nothing too exciting.

Ah cool.. GoDaddy was good and then it wasn't. Some people will dig working there as knowledge workers but management can be demanding and not know what they want/need... Of course that can happen anywhere.. GoDaddy does have some great tech problems to work on though.. :)
Nice. I keep hearing mixed thing about it. Good to know :)
